Questionnaire for trainer

What are the topics you're going to cover?

How many people are expected?

What environment will be available?

Will the participants have individual computers to work on?

Who is the audience? Freshers/junior - mid level developers / non developers (like testers)/ senior developers

Write down each topic and your confidence level in each

What are the examples you will use against each topic ?

How will you measure the effectiveness?

3 things you will do to encourage participation

3 things you will do to motivate trainees

3 things you will do to to make the class interesting

3 steps to improve your knowledge level in the run up to the training day and your progress against each - update daily

